        "description": {
            "value": "<p><span>This +2 greater striking shock rapier has a golden blade, and miniature electric arcs flash across its guard while itâ€™s wielded. When out of its sheath under an open sky, the blade causes storm clouds to gather slowly above.<br></span></p>\n<p><span><strong>Activate</strong> <span style=\"font-family: 'Pathfinder2eActions'; font-size: 1.8em; display: inline;\">D</span> command, envision; <strong>Frequency</strong> once per day; <strong>Effect</strong> You cast a 6th-level @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.9AAkVUCwF6WVNNY2]{Lightning Bolt} (DC 33). <br></span></p>\n<p><span><strong>Activate</strong> <span style=\"font-family: 'Pathfinder2eActions'; font-size: 1.8em; display: inline;\">R</span> command; <strong>Frequency</strong> once per 10 minutes; <strong>Trigger</strong> An electricity effect targets you or a creature within 10 feet of you, or has you or a creature within 10 feet of you in its area ; <strong>Effect</strong> You try to divert the electricity off course, to be absorbed by <em>storm flash</em>. Choose one eligible creature to protect and roll a melee attack roll against the DC of the electricity effect. If you succeed, the chosen creature takes no electricity damage from the triggering effect.&nbsp;</span></p>",
